Cell.Data: BEAst: This document describes the BEAst profile, and how BEAst's order response messages, version 3.1, for NeC, Rental and Material are linked to the Peppol structure. Peppol:
BEAst: T3345, Order response number. Peppol:
BEAst: T6099, Supplier's Order number. Peppol:
BEAst: T6114, Order response status. Peppol:
BEAst: T6008 and T6038, Transport information or Supplier's remark. Peppol:
Response message with amendments in the details

BEAst: The order response message always is preceeded by an order message. If the order response is a confirmation of something ordered by telephone, in a shop or a supplier portal, the Peppol message OrderAgreement should be used instead. Peppol:
BEAst: T3309 and T6335, Reference to the Order/Calloff. Peppol:
BEAst: T0009 or T6001, Identification of the Supplier. Peppol:
BEAst: T0009 or T6001, Identification of the Supplier. Peppol:
BEAst: T5001, Name of the Supplier. Peppol:
BEAst: T0008 or T6001, Identification of the Buyer. Peppol:
BEAst: T0008 or T6001, Identification of the Buyer. Peppol:
BEAst: T5001, Name of the Buyer. Peppol:
BEAst: Confirmation of delivery dates are always at line level, not here. Peppol:

BEAst: Orderlines should be included in the order response only when the OrderResponseCode is "CA" (Conditionally Accepted). For all other codes only the document header should be sent. When the order is Conditionally Accepted, all orderlines shall be included, not only those that are changed. Peppol:

BEAst: T6022, T6417 and T0172 if T6317 = "BP", Buyers part article number. Peppol:
BEAst: T0172, Supplier's article number. Peppol:

BEAst: Global Trade Item Number (T0154) or RSK Article Number Sweden (T6023). All other item number standards used within BEAst can not be used here until the organisation behind the standard decides to be a part of the codelist "ISO 6523 ICD". These are: NOBB Article Number (T6027), RT Article Number (T6460), TUN Article Number (T6028), Finfo/Vilma Article Number (T6029), Norwegian RSK Article Number (T6024), Norwegian E-number (T6026), E-number (T0260) and SGTIN (T6461). Peppol:
